onal-50-state-population-projections-2030-2040-2050%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprojected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20at%20least%20one%20in%20five%20US%20residents%20will%20be%2065%20or%20older.%20As%20US%20Census%20Bureau%20demographer%20Jonathan%20Vespa%20stated%20in%20a%20press%20release%2C%20that%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20in%20US%20history%20that%20older%20people%20would%20outnumber%20children.%20In%20light%20of%20those%20statistics%2C%20it%20seems%20many%20others%20may%20be%20joining%20me%20over%20here%20on%20the%20grandchildless%20side%20of%20the%20demographics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20actually%20never%20gave%20much%20thought%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20%E2%80%94%20or%20not%20being%20%E2%80%94%20a%20grandmother%20in%20the%20past.%20Though%20I%20wasn't%20pining%20away%20for%20my%20future%20grandchildren%2C%20it%20also%20always%20seemed%20like%20a%20given.%20The%20natural%20order%20of%20things%2C%20if%20you%20will.%20I%20thought%20I'd%20grow%20up%2C%20have%20kids%2C%20be%20a%20grandma%2C%20then%20die.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20thought%20it%20was%20simple%2C%20but%20it%20isn't.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e38bdd6f-a94e-4757-9b1d-e4ca5a2a585d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20kids%20would%20be%20great%20parents%2C%20but%20I%20respect%20their%20choice%20to%20remain%20child-free%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20kids%20are%20awesome%3B%20they%20are%20such%20cool%20people%20with%20unique%20outlooks%20on%20the%20world%2C%20and%20I%20think%20they%20both%20would%20have%20made%20amazing%20parents.%20However%2C%20I%20am%20100%25%20on%20board%20with%20their%20reasons%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstepmom-experience-didnt-want-kids-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20wanting%20any%20offspring%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20they%20told%20me%20they%20may%20not%20want%20to%20have%20kids%2C%20it%20wasn't%20a%20shocking%20revelation.%20They've%20pretty%20much%20always%20said%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20parents.%20When%20they%20were%20younger%2C%20I%20assumed%20they%20would%20change%20their%20minds%20as%20they%20aged.%20And%20mostly%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20major%20feelings%20about%20it.%20As%20it%20became%20clear%20it%20was%20not%20a%20phase%2C%20that%20neither%20of%20them%20would%20be%20having%20kids%20in%20the%20future%2C%20I%20still%20didn't%20have%20strong%20feelings.%20I%20know%20they%20are%20making%20reasonable%2C%20logical%20conclusions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3b5d430-2038-43a5-99ce-8724a19a218a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20future%20looks%20different%20from%20how%20I%20thought%20it%20would%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20still%20times%20when%20I%20see%20the%20elderly%20version%20of%20myself%20hanging%20out%20on%20my%20front%20porch%2C%20yelling%20at%20a%20gaggle%20of%20grandchildren%20to%20get%20out%20of%20my%20flowerbeds.%20(Note%3A%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20flowerbeds%2C%20either.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20time%20I%20%3Cem%3Esee%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20version%20of%20myself%2C%20I'm%20reminded%20that%20she%20will%20never%20be%20me.%20But%20It%20isn't%20grief%20exactly%2C%20more%20like%20a%20jarring%20type%20of%20confusion.%20My%20brain%20has%20to%20revise%20the%20list%20of%20things%20I%20thought%20I'd%20do%3A%20Grow%20up%20%E2%80%94check.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frealized-didnt-want-kids-after-seeing-friends-have-them-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHave%20kids%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20check.%20Be%20a%20grandma%20%E2%80%94%20nope.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20like%20my%20brain%20is%20buffering%2C%20trying%20to%20compute%20the%20data.%20There's%20still%20part%20of%20me%20that%20thinks%20that%20checklist%20