ed%20in%20areas%20around%20the%20City%20Palace%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishvaraj%20Singh%20was%20anointed%20titular%20head%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Mewar%20royal%20family%20on%20Monday%20at%20a%20ceremony%20in%20Chittorgarh%20Fort%20following%20his%20father's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20offer%20prayer%20at%20a%20'dhuni'%20(sacred%20fire)%20in%20the%20City%20Palace%20premises%20and%20then%20to%20Eklingnath%20Temple%20to%20finish%20the%20ritual%20However%2C%20his%20uncle%20Arvind%20Singh%20Mewar%20through%20his%20lawyer%20got%20two%20public%20notices%20published%20in%20newspapers%20on%20Monday%2C%20prohibiting%20unauthorised%20entry%20to%20the%20palace%20and%20Eklingnathji%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20said%20that%20Shree%20Eklingji%20Trust%20Udaipur%20has%20decided%20to%20give%20entry%20to%20the%20temple%20on%20November%2025%20to%20only%20those%20authorised%20by%20the%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Singh%20Mewar%2C%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Mewar's%20younger%20brother%2C%20is%20the%20trust's%20chairman%20and%20managing%20trustee.%20The%20City%20Palace%20is%20also%20under%20his%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20notices%20appeared%2C%20policemen%20were%20deployed%20at%20the%20entry%20gate%20of%20the%20palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20was%20denied%20entry%2C%20violent%20protests%20erupted%20following%20which%20the%20district%20administration%20appointed%20a%20receiver%20on%20Monday%20night%20for%20the%20controversial%20portion%20of%20the%20Palace%20where%20'Dhuni'%20is%20situated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20returned%20to%20his%20residence%20without%20performing%20the%20ritual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stalemate%20between%20Vishvaraj%20and%20Arvind%20Singh%20Mewar's%20family%20continued%20yesterday%20with%20Vishvaraj%20and%20Arvind%20Singh%20Mewar's%20son%20Lakshyaraj%20Singh%20targeting%20each%20other%20without%20naming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshyaraj%20Singh%20told%20the%20media%20last%20night%20that%20endangering%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20ritual%20was%20not%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20some%20people%20in%20government%20posts%20were%20mounting%20pressure%20on%20the%20administration%20for%20their%20vested%20interest%20and%20were%20trying%20to%20forcefully%20enter%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshyaraj%20Singh%20suggested%20that%20if%20someone%20wants%20to%20seek%20entry%3B%20he%20should%20go%20to%20the%20court.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Eklingnathji%20temple%20is%20open%20to%20the%20public%20and%20anyone%20can%20go%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENegotiations%20are%20continuing%20for%20facilitating%20Vishvaraj%20Singh's%20entry%20to%20the%20palace%20for%20dhuni%20darshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESP%20Yogesh%20Goyal%20informed%20that%20some%20senior%20officers%20have%20arrived%20in%20Udaipur%20to%20resolve%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732702320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fjiets28_udaipur_625x300_26_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-deadlock-udaipurs-maharana-vishvaraj-singh-visits-palace-temple-to-complete-rituals-7117482%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20deadlock%20over%20entry%20to%20Udaipur%20City%20Palace%20to%20have%20darshan%20of%20'dhuni'%20after%20his%20coronation%20ceremony%2C%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%20on%20Wednesday%20reached%20Eklingnathji%20temple%20to%20complete%20his%20father's%20mourning%20rituals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-deadlock-udaipurs-maharana-vishvaraj-singh-visits-palace-temple-to-complete-rituals-7117482%22%2C%22cdnAm