20President-elect's%20fondness%20for%20tariffs%20as%20a%20negotiating%20tool%2C%20it's%20particularly%20troubling%20that%20he's%20threatening%20to%20aim%20them%20at%20America's%20closest%20allies%20and%20trading%20partners%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%20of%20his%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChrystia%20Freeland%2C%20the%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20of%20Canada%2C%20and%20Dominic%20LeBlanc%2C%20the%20country's%20public%20safety%20minister%2C%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20on%20Monday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDLeBlancNB%2Fstatus%2F1861239067070910802%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponded%20to%20Trump's%20remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20they%20touted%20the%20mutually%20beneficial%20alliance%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanada%20and%20the%20United%20States%20have%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20and%20closest%20relationships%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20trade%20and%20border%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20officials%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BCanada%20places%20the%20highest%20priority%20on%20border%20security%20and%20the%20integrity%20of%20our%20shared%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20addition%2C%20the%20CBSA%20%5BCanada%20Border%20Services%20Agency%5D%20is%20continually%20strengthening%20its%20ability%20to%20detect%20opioids%20through%20enhanced%20inspections%20at%20ports%20of%20entry%2C%20detector%20dogs%2C%20and%20emerging%20technologies%2C%20preventing%20opioids%20from%20entering%20and%20leaving%20Canada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20then%20pledged%20to%20work%20with%20Trump's%20second-term%20administration%20in%20tackling%20the%20issues%20that%20he%20raised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20a%20representative%20of%20Trump%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-us-canada-tariffs-