s.%20Some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20innovative%20companies%20were%20basically%20next%20door%2C%20and%20their%20corporate%20headquarters%20lined%20the%20city's%20blocks%20like%20Lego%20bricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20once%20interviewed%20at%20Salesforce's%20headquarters%20while%20on%20my%20lunch%20break%20since%20it%20was%20only%20a%20few%20blocks%20away%20from%20PwC.%20When%20doing%20phone%20screens%20for%20Uber%2C%20Twitter%2C%20and%20Dolby%2C%20I%20knew%20I'd%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20over%20to%20their%20offices%20for%20an%20on-site%20interview%20at%20a%20moment's%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20young%20professional%20with%20limited%20life%20responsibilities%2C%20San%20Francisco%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20live%20fast%20and%20loose.%20The%20social%20scene%20was%20amazing%20%E2%80%94%20a%20night%20out%20for%20drinks%20could%20mean%20stopping%20by%20a%20speakeasy%20with%20no%20sign%2C%20sipping%20a%20mai%20tai%20on%20a%20floating%20tiki%20bar%2C%20or%20drinks%20served%20from%20a%20bathtub%20at%20a%20bar%20the%20size%20of%20a%20walk-in%20closet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco%20also%20has%20the%20best%20park%20scene%20in%20the%20country%3B%20I've%20yet%20to%20find%20a%20better%20party%20than%20a%20regular%20Saturday%20afternoon%20at%20Dolores%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222650%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20sit%20on%20the%20grass%20of%20Mission%20Dolores%20Park%20overlooking%20the%20San%20Francisco%20skyline%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6744fee0ede4eeae39297894%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221471%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20afternoon%20in%20Dolores%20Park.%3Cp%3EMike%20Manalac%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-walkable-city-upsized-after-retirement-moved-to-suburbs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalkable%20city%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20adult%20life%2C%20I%20was%20car-free.%20The%20city%20was%20full%20of%20trendy%20coffee%20shops%2C%20unique%20bars%20and%20restaurants%2C%20and%20charming%20neighborhoods%20to%20explore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20living%20in%20San%20Francisco%20also%20isn't%20for%20the%20faint%20of%20heart.%20Outside%20of%20coworkers%2C%20my%20then-fianc%C3%A9e%20(and%20now%20wife)%20and%20I%20found%20it%20incredibly%20challenging%20to%20make%20friends%3B%20everyone%20seemed%20to%20assign%20others%20a%20level%20of%20importance%20based%20on%20where%20they%20lived%20and%20worked.%20I%20also%20would've%20needed%20an%20absurd%20amount%20of%20wealth%20to%20purchase%20a%20home%20and%20raise%20a%20family%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20that%20the%20city's%20biggest%20blemish%2C%20though%2C%20was%20the%20seedy%20Tenderloin%20district%2C%20which%20sits%20smack%20dab%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20downtown.%20I%20had%20to%20walk%20through%20the%20neighborhood%20to%20catch%20a%20corporate%20shuttle%20bus%20to%20work%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20my%20fair%20share%20of%20sketchy%20characters%20and%20shady%20dealings%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257e5599e-ed6a-4242-9220-76ecfff030a8%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley's%20career%20opportunities%20were%20unmatched%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20year%2C%20I%20started%20working%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20after%20I%20joined%20Walmart's%20eCommerce%20division%20in%20San%20Bruno.%20And%20the%20following%20year%2C%20I%20landed%20a%20job%20as%20an%20accounting%20manager%20at%20Google's%20Sunnyvale%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESilicon%20Valley%20offers%20the%20coolest%20places%20to%20work%20and%20its%20career%20opportunities%20are%20unmatched.%20I%20was%20amazed%20by%20the%20sprawling%20corporate%20campuses.%20Walking%20through%20Facebook's%20invite-only%20campus%2C%20which%20is%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-new-campus-pictures-2015-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalled%20garden%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20down%20its%20main%20street%2C%20Hacker%20Way%2C%20I%20was%20in%20awe.%20In%20nearby%20Mountain%20View%2C%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20how%20nearly%20every%20building%20in%20the%20city%20was%20branded%20with%20Google's%20logo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Manalac%20takes%20a%20selfie%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Google%20Android%20Statue%20Garden%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6744ff1cfa0140cdd5655b83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EManalac%20at%20Google's%20Android%20Statue%20Garden%20in%20July%202018.%3Cp%3EMike%20Manalac%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20corporate%20buses%20and%20colorful%20bikes%20whizzing%20around%20and%20young%20professionals%20with%20corporate%20badges%20on%20their%20hips%20and%20branded%20backpacks%20on%20their%20backs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Silicon%20Valley%20may%20be%20the%20tech%20capital%20of%20the%20world%2C%20I'd%20never%20live%20there.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20it%3B%20the%20cookie-cutter%20neighborhoods%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20are%20reserved%20for%20millionaires%20and%20the%20hillside%20mansions%20for%20billionaires.%20I%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdream-job-google-great-perks-nightmare-commute-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommuted%20from%20San%20Francisco%3C%2Fa%3E%20via%20corporate%20shuttle%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20wanted%20to%20live%20there%20anyway.%20The%20social%20scene%20was%20dead%2C%20the%20city%20wasn't%20walkable%2C%20and%20the%20nightlife%20was%20nonexistent.%20Nobody%20I%20knew%20went%20to%20happy%20hour%20after%20work%2C%20restaurants%20closed%20early%2C%20and%20most%20people%20only%20lived%20there%20because%20of%20the%20proximity%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230fec277-4d64-420b-8cf9-04ac7681f26a%5C%22%3EChicago%20has%20a%20down-to-earth%20social%20scene%20and%20affordable%2C%20family-friendly%20neighborhoods%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Chicago%20with%20my%20wife%20in%202019%2C%20transferring%20to%20Google's%20Chicago%20office.%20The%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Chicago%20was%20much%20cheaper%2C%20my%20commute%20would%20be%20shorter%2C%20and%20we'd%20be%20closer%20to%20her%20family%20in%20Michigan%20and%20mine%20in%20Maryland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChicago%20doesn't%20have%20the%20buzzy%20tech%20scene%20or%20beautiful%20weather%20of%20San%20Francisco%20and%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20but%20it's%20no%20slouch%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20career%20opportunities.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F06%2F09%2Fwhat-city-has-most-fortune-500-corporate-headquarters-winners-losers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMore%20Fortune%20500%20companies%20are%20headquartered%20in%20Chicago%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20in%20almost%20every%20other%20city%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20job%20opportunities%20are%20much%20more%20diverse%20than%20what%20you'll%20find%20in%20the%20tech-centric%20San%20Francisco%20and%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Google's%20office%20in%20Chicago's%20West%20Loop%2C%20I%20can%20see%20McDonald's%20global%20headquarters%20down%20the%20street%20and%20a%20number%20of%20other%20premier%20employers%20dotting%20the%20city%20skyline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChicago%20is%20a%20city%20that%20likes%20to%20party%2C%20making%20San%20Francisco%20look%20sleepy%20by%20comparison.%20Bars%20don't%20close%20until%202%20a.m.%2C%20with%20some%20staying%20open%20until%204%20a.m.%20Chicago's%20Lake%20Michigan%20beach%20scene%20is%20much%20livelier%20than%20that%20of%20San%20Francisco.%20But%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-chicago-from-portland-big-city-life-affordable-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20social%20scene%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20has%20a%20down-to-earth%20vibe%3B%20people%20are%20Midwest%20nice%20and%20seem%20to%20live%20at%20a%20more%20casual%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20about%20Chicago%20is%20the%20moderate%20cost%20of%20living.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20afford%20a%20three-unit%20home%20with%20rental%20potential%20in%20Chicago%20for%20%24830%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20a%20price%20I'd%20never%20find%20in%20San%20Francisco%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20in%20a%20walkable%20neighborhood.%20It's%20the%20perfect%20blend%20of%20family-friendly%20city%20life.%20Our%20three-year-old%20son%20loves%20taking%20the%20train%20home%20from%20daycare%20and%20running%20wild%20at%20one%20of%20the%20city's%20many%20playgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d77c25a7-65ab-4865-a872-dbef1350787f%5C%22%3EI%20think%20Chicago%20is%20the%20best%20of%20the%20three%20places%20to%20start%20a%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20in%20these%20three%20awesome%20places%2C%20I've%20realized%20that%20even%20the%20best%20cities%20have%20their%20flaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco%20has%20the%20coolest%20social%20scene%20and%20overall%20vibe%2C%20but%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20cities%20for%20settling%20down%20because%20of%20its%20high%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESilicon%20Valley%20offers%20the%20best%20career%20opportunities%2C%20but%20its%20social%20scene%20is%20lacking%20since%20everything%20there%20is%20about%20work%2C%20work%2C%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChicago%20is%20the%20best%20of%20the%20three%20locations%20to%20start%20a%20family%20due%20to%20its%20affordability%20and%20comfortable%20pace%20of%20life%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20quite%20as%20cool%20as%20San%20Francisco%20and%20can't%20match%20the%20career%20opportunities%20offered%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20though%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20beat%20Chicago's%20mix%20of%20career%20opportunities%2C%20vibrant%20social%20scene%2C%20and%20opportunities%20to%20start%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you've%20moved%20around%20for%20work%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20experiences%20of%20different