d%20all%20three%20Mahayuti%20partners%20are%20still%20deciding%20and%20an%20answer%20will%20be%20given%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20wants%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20for%20the%20top%20job%2C%20its%20ally%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20rooting%20for%20its%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde.%20The%20BJP%20is%20now%20holding%20backroom%20talks%20with%20its%20ally%20to%20iron%20out%20differences%20and%20prevent%20embarrassment%20once%20it%20names%20its%20choice%20for%20the%20top%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Opposition%20has%20been%20questioning%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20Mahayuti%20naming%20its%20Chief%20Minister%20pick%2C%20BJP%20sources%20say%20they%20were%20in%20no%20rush%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20looking%20at%20any%20timeline.%20The%20government%20formation%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20took%20two%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%2C%20the%20leaders%20of%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20also%20need%20to%20reach%20an%20agreement%20on%20ministerial%20berths.%20Maharashtra%20can%20have%20a%20total%20of%2043%20ministers%2C%20including%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%20132%20out%20of%20the%20Mahayuti's%20score%20of%20230%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20claim%20half%20of%20the%20ministerial%20berths%2C%20leaving%20the%20rest%20for%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20toppled%20in%202022%20due%20to%20a%20mutiny%20led%20by%20Mr%20Shinde%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20backed%20him%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20despite%20holding%20more%20numerical%20heft%20in%20the%20Assembly.%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20albeit%20grudgingly%2C%20had%20accepted%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20role.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20after%20its%20stellar%20show%20in%20the%20polls%2C%20BJP%20is%20unlikely%20to%20let%20the%20post%20go%20to%20its%20ally.%20According%20to%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20party%20workers%20want%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20in%20the%20top%20role.%20The%20BJP's%20ideological%20parent%20RSS%20is%20also%20backing%20the%20Nagpur%20South%20West%20MLA%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEknath%20Shinde%20%26quot%3BUnhappy%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamdas%20Athawale%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20leader%20of%20BJP%20ally%20Republican%20Party%20of%20India%20(Athawale)%2C%20has%20backed%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20want%20him.%26quot%3B%20Admitting%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20question%20has%20led%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeadlock%26quot%3B%20within%20the%20Mahayuti%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Eknath%20Shinde%20came%20to%20know%20that%20the%20BJP%20high%20command%20has%20finalised%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20as%20the%20CM%2C%20he%20was%20unhappy.%20And%20I%20can%20understand%20that.%20But%2C%20BJP%20has%20got%20132%20seats...%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20should%20be%20made%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20leaders%20have%20said%20the%20election%20was%20won%20under%20Mr%20Shinde's%20leadership%20and%20he%20must%20continue%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20Earlier%2C%20Sena%20spokesperson%20Naresh%20Mhaske%20cited%20the%20'Bihar%20model'.%20%26quot%3BWe%20feel%20Shinde%20should%20be%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20just%20like%20in%20Bihar%20where%20BJP%20did%20not%20look%20at%20the%20numbers%20but%20still%20made%20JD(U)%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar%20the%20CM.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Sena%20leader%20and%20MLA%20Sanjay%20Shirsat%20said%20Mr%20Shinde's%20face%20played%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20Mahayuti's%20victory.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20made%20sacrifices.%20We%20left%20power.%20Serious%20allegations%20were%20made%2C%20but%20we%20rose%20above%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20Fires%20Barbs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20Mahayuti%20announcing%20its%20Chief%20Minister%20pick%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20has%20started%20taking%20swipes%20at%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20who%20led%20the%20rebellion%20that%20split%20the%20Sena%20and%20toppled%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20poll%20results%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20had%20said%20Mr%20Shinde%20would%20now%20have%20to%20work%20under%20Mr%20Fadnavis.%20Amid%20reports%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20chosen%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20for%20the%20top%20job%2C%20Sena%20(UBT)%20has%20stepped%20up%20its%20attack.%20Mr%20Thackeray's%20aide%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Raut%20has%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEknath%20Shinde%20won't%20become%20Chief%20Minister.%20His%20purpose%20has%20been%20served.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raut%20also%20claimed%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20mandate%20of%20the%20people%2C%20but%20of%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESena%20(UBT)%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Devendra%20Fadnavis'%20name%20has%20been%20finalised%2C%20announce%20it%20quickly%3B%20what%20is%20stopping%20you%3F%20Why%20are%20you%20depriving%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20of%20the%20promises%20made%20to%20them%2C%20why%20are%20you%20keeping%20them%20away%20and%20why%20are%20you%20ignoring%20the%20steering%20crisis%20of%20Maharashtra%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESena%20Says%20Mahayuti%20United%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20strong%20score%20in%20this%20election%20has%20put%20it%20in%20an%20advantageous%20position%20and%20it%20now%20needs%20only%20one%20of%20its%20two%20allies%20--%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20--%20to%20support%20it%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20And%20the%20NCP%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20has%20already%20thrown%20its%20weight%20behind%20Mr%20Fadnavis.%20So%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20has%20little%20leverage%20to%20bargain%20hard%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%20The%20party%20is%20likely%20to%20demand%20a%20good%20deal%20in%20ministerial%20posts%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Sena%20MP%20Naresh%20Mhaske%20said%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20will%20be%20taken%20very%20soon.%20However%2C%20he%20clarified%20that%20the%20Mahayuti%20is%20united.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20suspense.%20Mahayuti's%20leader%20will%20become%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20media%20is%20in%20a%20hurry.%20Government%20formation%20takes%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20that%20we%20will%20run%20away%20if%20Chief%20Ministership%20is%20not%20given%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Sena-BJP%20split%20after%20the%202019%20state%20polls%20when%20Mr%20Thackeray%20ended%20the%20alliance%20due%20to%20differences%20over%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732698060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fp9sgdg94_shinde-fadnavis-650_625x300_04_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-maharashtra-election-results-eknath-shinde-devendra-fadnavis-opposition-questions-maharashtra-chief-minister-suspense-bjp-says-no-rush-7116608%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20days%20have%20passed%20since%20the%20Mahayuti%20scored%20a%20mammoth%20win%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20but%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20Chief%20Minister%20choice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-maharashtra-election-results-eknath-shinde-devendra-fadnavis-opposition-questions-maharashtra-chief-minister-suspense-bjp-says-no-rush-7116608%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Euphoria%20star%20Barbie%20Ferreira's%20SHOCKING%20weight%20loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732698007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-11