%2Fgoldman-sachs-sees-gold-at-3-150-per-ounce-oil-at-100-a-barrel-in-2025-124112700549_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thus%20far%20in%20calendar%20year%202024%20(CY24)%2C%20Brent%20crude%20oil%20prices%20hit%20a%20low%20of%20around%20%2469%20a%20barrel%20before%20breaching%20the%20%2491%20a%20barrel%20mark%20in%20April%202024%20as%20geopolitical%20concerns%20rose%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fgoldman-sachs-sees-gold-at-3-150-per-ounce-oil-at-100-a-barrel-in-2025-124112700549_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOur%20Sensitivities%20Different...%26quot%3B%3A%20Minister%20On%20'Vulgar'%20Social%20Media%20Content%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20effort%20to%20combat%20'vulgar'%20content%20on%20social%20media%20and%20OTT%20platforms%20require%20strengthening%20of%20existing%20laws%2C%20Union%20Information%20%26amp%3B%20Broadcasting%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20told%20Parliament%20Wednesday%2C%20declaring%20such%20to%20be%20the%20result%20of%20%26quot%3Bdifferences%20between%20our%20culture%20and%20the%20culture%20of%20countries%20from%20these%20platforms%20come%20(referring%20obliquely%20to%20the%20West)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20Zero%20Hour%20question%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Arun%20Govil%20about%20laws%20to%20check%20'abusive'%20content%20online%2C%20including%20that%20on%20social%20media%20and%20available%20on%20OTT%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20difference%20between%20the%20(cultural)%20sensitivities%20in%20our%20country%20and%20the%20countries%20from%20where%20these%20platforms%20come.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20like%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20to%20take%20up%20this%20issue...%20the%20existing%20law%20needs%20to%20be%20strengthened%2C%20and%20I%20request%20a%20consensus%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%20also%20blamed%20the%20lack%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Beditorial%20check%26quot%3B%20on%20content%20posted%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20the%20way%20editorial%20content%20used%20to%20be...%20an%20editorial%20check%20used%20to%20be%20done%2C%20if%20something%20is%20'right'%20or%20'wrong'...%20has%20ended.%20Social%20media%2C%20today%2C%20is%20a%20big%20medium%20of%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%20but%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20due%20to%20the%20end%20of%20that%20editorial%20check%2C%20vulgar%20content%20is%20also%20played.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister%20spoke%20after%20Mr%20Govil%20-%20an%20actor%20who%20made%20his%20name%20playing%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20the%20hugely%20popular%20Ramayan%20TV%20series%20-%20claimed%20content%20on%20social%20media%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20match%20Indian%20culture%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20for%20a%20government%20watchdog%20to%20%26quot%3Bkeep%20a%20close%20eye%26quot%3B%20on%20material%20posted%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20comes%20a%20month%20after%20his%20deputy%2C%20L%20Murugan%2C%20confirmed%20the%20government%20is%20drafting%20a%20new%20policy%20to%20regulate%20OTT%20content%3B%20this%20is%20aimed%20at%20non-self-regulating%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20federal%20election%20-%20Mr%20Vaishnaw's%20predecessor%2C%20Anurag%20Thakur%2C%20blocked%2018%20OTT%20apps%20for%20publishing%20%26quot%3Bobscene%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bvulgar%2C%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20in%20some%20instances%2C%20%26quot%3Bpornographic%20content%26quot%3B.%20They%20were%20also%20found%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Bportrayed%20women%20in%20a%20demeaning%20manner%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quest%20to%20identify%20and%20eliminate%20'vulgar'%20content%20online%20-%20the%20definition%20of%20what%20is%20and%20what%20isn't%20vulgar%2C%20apart%20from%20that%20identified%20as%20illegal%20under%20existing%20laws%2C%20is%20not%20clear%20-%20has%20played%20out%20often%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20including%20in%20challenges%20to%20OTT%20platforms%20like%20Netflix%20and%20Prime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20massive%20row%20in%20September%20over%20a%20Netflix%20web%20series%20on%20the%201999%20hijacking%20of%20an%20Indian%20Airlines%20flight%20by%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20outfit%20Harkat-ul-Mujahideen.%20A%20row%20over%20the%20changing%20of%20two%20of%20the%20terrorists'%20names%20led%20to%20protests%20and%20the%20government%20stepped%20in%2C%20after%20which%20Netflix%20said%20future%20content%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bin%20accordance%20with%20the%20nation's%20sentiments%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%20last%20year%20the%20government%20also%20told%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20its%20policy%20governing%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20intermediaries%20will%20incorporate%20necessary%20rules%20and%20regulations%20to%20ensure%20the%20space%20occupied%20by%20them%20is%20free%20from%20vulgar%20language%20and%20profanities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20said%20the%20challenge%20faced%20by%20India%2C%20as%20by%20many%20other%20countries%2C%20for%20enacting%20appropriate%20law%2C%20guidelines%20and%20rules%20to%20regulate%20the%20content%20on%20social%20media%20and%20OTT%20platforms%20needs%20urgent%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732697340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fopfvkq98_ashwini-vaishnaw_625x300_20_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashwini-vaishnaw-vulgar-content-social-media-ott-platforms-our-sensitivities-different-minister-on-vulgar-social-media-content-7116864%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government's%20effort%20to%20combat%20'vulgar'%20content%20on%20social%20media%20and%20OTT%20platforms%20require%20strengthening%20of%20existing%20laws%2C%20Union%20Information%20%26amp%3B%20Broadcasting%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20told%20Parliament%2