3Cp%3EBefore%20it%20started%2C%2056-year-old%20Kim%20Yun-suk%20fell%20asleep%20to%20the%20hum%20of%20insects%20and%20woke%20to%20the%20chirping%20of%20birds.%20Now%2C%20she%20is%20kept%20awake%20every%20night%20by%20what%20sounds%20like%20the%20soundtrack%20of%20a%20low-budget%20horror%20movie%20at%20top%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20peaceful%20sounds%20of%20nature...%20have%20now%20been%20drowned%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20we%20hear%20is%20this%20noise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign%20is%20the%20latest%20manifestation%20of%20steadily%20declining%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20Koreas%20this%20year%2C%20which%20have%20also%20seen%20Pyongyang%20test%20ever%20more%20powerful%20missiles%20and%20bombard%20the%20South%20with%20trash-carrying%20balloons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20July%2C%20North%20Korea%20has%20been%20broadcasting%20the%20noises%20for%20huge%20chunks%20of%20almost%20every%20day%20from%20loudspeakers%20along%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20northern%20point%20of%20Ganghwa%20--%20an%20island%20in%20the%20Han%20river%20estuary%20on%20the%20Yellow%20Sea%20--%20is%20only%20about%20two%20kilometres%20(a%20mile)%20from%20the%20North.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20AFP%20visited%2C%20the%20nighttime%20broadcast%20included%20what%20sounded%20like%20the%20screams%20of%20people%20dying%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20the%20crack%20of%20gunfire%2C%20bombs%20exploding%2C%20along%20with%20chilling%20music%20that%20started%20at%2011%3A00%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20almost%20pitch-black%20fields%2C%20sinister%20noises%20echoed%20as%20the%20stars%20in%20the%20clear%20night%20sky%20shone%20beautifully%20alongside%20the%20coastal%20road%20lights%2C%20creating%20a%20stark%20and%20unsettling%20contrast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea%20has%20done%20propaganda%20broadcasts%20before%2C%20said%2066-year-old%20villager%20Ahn%20Hyo-cheol%2C%20but%20they%20used%20to%20focus%20on%20criticising%20the%20South's%20leaders%2C%20or%20idealising%20the%20North.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20%26quot%3Bthere%20were%20sounds%20like%20a%20wolf%20howling%2C%20and%20ghostly%20sounds%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20unpleasant%20and%20gives%20me%20chills.%20It%20really%20feels%20bizarre.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanghwa%20county%20councillor%20Park%20Heung-yeol%20said%20the%20new%20broadcasts%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20just%20regime%20propaganda%20--%20it's%20genuinely%20intended%20to%20torment%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETorture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20said%20the%20new%20broadcasts%20almost%20meet%20the%20criteria%20for%20a%20torture%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlmost%20every%20regime%20has%20used%20noise%20torture%20and%20sleep%20deprivation%2C%26quot%3B%20Rory%20Cox%2C%20a%20historian%20at%20the%20University%20of%20St%20Andrews%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20common%20and%20leaves%20no%20physical%20scarring%2C%20therefore%20making%20it%20deniable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExposure%20to%20noise%20levels%20above%2060%20decibels%20at%20night%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20sleep%20disorders%2C%20experts%20said%2C%20but%20AFP%20tracked%20levels%20of%20up%20to%2080%20decibels%20late%20at%20night%20on%20Ganghwa%20during%20a%20recent%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20find%20myself%20taking%20headache%20medicine%20almost%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20An%20Mi-hee%2C%2037%2C%20told%20AFP%2C%20adding%20that%20prolonged%20sleep%20deprivation%20due%20to%20the%20noise%20has%20also%20led%20to%20anxiety%2C%20eye%20pain%2C%20facial%20tremors%20and%20drowsiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20kids%20can't%20sleep%20either%2C%20so%20they've%20developed%20mouth%20sores%20and%20are%20dozing%20off%20at%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistraught%20and%20desperate%2C%20An%20travelled%20to%20Seoul%20and%20got%20on%20her%20knees%20to%20beg%20lawmakers%20at%20the%20National%20Assembly%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20breaking%20down%20in%20tears%20as%20she%20described%20the%20island's%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20actually%20be%20better%20if%20there%20were%20a%20flood%2C%20a%20fire%2C%20or%20even%20an%20earthquake%2C%20because%20those%20events%20have%20a%20clear%20recovery%20timeline%2C%26quot%3B%20An%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20idea%20if%20this%20will%20go%20on%20until%20the%20person%20in%20North%20Korea%20who%20gives%20the%20orders%20dies%2C%20or%20if%20it%20could%20be%20cut%20off%20at%20any%20moment.%20We%20just%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'70s%20horror%20flick'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20noise%20tormenting%20Ganghwa%20island%20residents%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20rudimentary%20mix%20of%20clips%20from%20a%20sound%20library%2C%20typically%20common%20at%20any%20TV%20or%20radio%20broadcasters%2C%20audio%20experts%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sound%20effects%20are%20%26quot%3Blike%20something%20found%20in%20a%20South%20Korean%20horror%20film%20in%20the%2070s%20and%2080s%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20sound%20engineer%20Hwang%20Kwon-ik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Koreas%20remain%20technically%20at%20war%20since%20the%201950%20to%201953%20conflict%20ended%20in%20an%20armistice%20not%20a%20peace%20treaty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20this%20year%20declared%20Seoul%20his%20%26quot%3Bprincipal%20enemy%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20ramped%20up%20weapons%20testing%20and%20built%20closer%20military%20ties%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20isolated%20and%20impoverished%20North%20is%20known%20to%20be%20extremely%20sensitive%20about%20its%20citizens%20gaining%20access%20to%20South%20Korean%20pop%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20have%20suggested%20the%20latest%20broadcasts%20could%20be%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20North%20Korean%20soldiers%20from%20hearing%20the%20South's%20own%20propaganda%20broadcasts%2C%20which%20typically%20feature%20K-pop%20songs%20and%20international%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20just%20weeks%20after%20South%20Korea%20resumed%20K-pop%20broadcasts%20in%20response%20to%20Pyongyang%20floating%20trash-carrying%20balloons%20south%2C%20a%20North%20Korean%20soldier%20defected%20by%20crossing%20the%20heavily%20fortified%20border%20on%20foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Lee%20Su-yong%2C%20an%20audio%20production%20professor%20at%20the%20Dong-Ah%20Institute%20of%20Media%20and%20Arts%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20sound%20coming%20towards%20the%20North%20that%20you%20want%20to%20mask%2C%20then%20the%20sound%20(you%20use%20to%20cover%20it)%20must%20also%20be%20directed%20toward%20the%20North.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20less%20about%20masking%20noise%20and%20more%20about%20inflicting%20pain%20on%20people%20in%20the%20South%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoi%20Hyoung-chan%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20resident%2C%20said%20the%20South%20Korean%20government%20had%20failed%20to%20protect%20vulnerable%20civilians%20on%20the%20frontier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20come%20here%20and%20try%20to%20live%20with%20these%20sounds%20for%20just%20ten%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP%2C%20referring%20to%20officials%20in%20Seoul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20doubt%20they%20could%20even%20endure%20a%20single%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732694160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fitt04j0g_north-korea_625x300_27_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgunshots-screams-evil-laugh-north-koreas-new-weapon-is-bloodcurdling-sounds-7116269%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22South%20Korea's%20border%20island%20Ganghwa%20is%20being%20bombarded%20nightly%20with%20blood-curdling%20sounds%2C%20part%20of%20a%20new%20campaign%20by%20the%20nuclear-armed%20North%20that%20is%20driving%20residents%20to%20despair.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgunshots-screams-evil-laugh-north-koreas-new-weapon-is-bloodcurdling-sounds-7116269%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Killing%20Vlogger%20In%20Bengaluru%2C%20Boyfriend%20Spent%202%20Days%20Smoking%20Near%20Corpse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20vlogger%20from%20Assam%20allegedly%20by%20her%20paramour%2C%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20killer%20spent%20two%20days%20with%20the%20corpse%20of%20Maya%20Gogoi%2C%20at%20a%20service%20apartment%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20police%20sources%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shocking%20incident%20had%20come%20to%20light%20in%20Indiranagar%20police%20station%20limits%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fman-stabs-girlfriend-to-death-in-bengaluru-hotel-stays-with-body-for-a-day-7111005%5C%22%3Eprobe%20so%20far%20has%20revealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20boyfriend-turned-alleged%20killer%20Aarav%20Hanoy%20had%20spent%20two%20days%20with%20the%20body%20of%20Maya%20Gogoi%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20time%20he%20was%20just%20smoking%20cigarettes%20while%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20the%20corpse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20formed%20two%20teams%20and%20launched%20a%20manhunt%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspected%20killer's%20phone%20is%20switched%20off%20and%20police%20teams%20are%20searching%20for%20him%20in%20Kerala%20and%20other%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAarav%20Hanoy%2C%20after%20boarding%20a%20taxi%20from%20the%20service%20apartment%2C%20had%20reached%20the%20Majestic%20area%20located%20in%20the%20Central%20Business%20District%20of%20Bengaluru%20and%20turned%20off%20his%20phone%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20deceased%20vlogger%20Maya%20lived%20with%20her%20sister%20in%20Bengaluru's%20HSR%20Layout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaya%20had%20called%20her%20sister%20and%20informed%20her%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20come%20home%20as%20she%20was%20attending%20an%20office%20party%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20she%20had%20sent%20another%20message%20on%20Saturday%20stating%20that%20she%20would%20not%20come%20to%20the%20residence%20as%20she%20was%20partying%20on%20that%20night%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaya's%20sister%20has%20told%20the%20police%20that%20Aarav%20and%20Maya%20were%20in%20a%20relationship%20for%20the%20last%20six%20months%20after%20meeting%20via%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20checked%20into%20the%20service%20apartment%20on%20Saturday%20and%20an%20initial%20probe%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20brought%20a%20knife%20with%20him%20while%20checking%20into%20the%20service%20apartment.%20He%20had%20also%20purchased%20a%20nylon%20rope%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20time%20with%20Maya%2C%20the%20accused%20had%20stabbed%20her%20to%20death%2C%20police%20sources%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20gathered%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20information%20about%20the%20cab%20he%20booked%20and%20the%20time%20he%20went%20out%20from%20the%20service%20apartment%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20had%20left%20the%20service%20apartment%20at%208.19%20A.M.%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20the%20police%20suspected%20that%20the%20killer%20had%20spent%20an%20entire%20day%20with%20his%20lover's%20corpse%20in%20a%20rented%20room%20before%20coolly%20strolling%20out%20and%20disappearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20it%20has%20emerged%20that%20he%20spent%20two%20days%20with%20the%20corpse%20as%20Maya%20and%20Aarav%20had%20bo