y%20claimed%20that%20Paty%20had%20asked%20Muslim%20students%20to%20leave%20his%20classroom%20before%20showing%20caricatures%20of%20the%20prophet%20Mohammed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20not%20in%20the%20classroom%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20apologise%20to%20the%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2017-year-old%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20named%2C%20told%20the%20court.%20%26quot%3BI%20destroyed%20your%20lives%2C%20I%20am%20sorry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20trial%20is%20Abdelhakim%20Sefrioui%2C%20a%2065-year-old%20French-Moroccan%20Islamist%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20Chnina%20spread%20the%20teenager's%20lies%20on%20social%20networks%20with%20the%20aim%2C%20according%20to%20the%20prosecution%2C%20of%20%26quot%3Bdesignating%20a%20target%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bprovoking%20a%20feeling%20of%20hatred%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthus%20preparing%20several%20crimes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20men%20have%20been%20in%20pre-trial%20detention%20for%20the%20past%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20told%20the%20court%20that%20she%20lied%20to%20her%20mother%20to%20justify%20why%20she%20had%20been%20suspended%20from%20school%20for%20two%20days%20over%20her%20behaviour%20and%20repeated%20absences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20panic%20and%20stress%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20her%20I%20had%20been%20in%20class%20and%20that%20I%20wasn't%20happy%20with%20what%20went%20on%20there%20and%20that%20the%20teacher%20excluded%20me.%20That%20we%20looked%20at%20cartoons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'I%20thought%20somebody%20would%20stop%20me'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESefrioui%20posted%20a%20video%20describing%20Paty%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bteaching%20thug%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20staged%20an%20%26quot%3Binterview%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20teenager%20outside%20the%20school%2C%20whispering%20to%20her%20what%20to%20answer.%20The%20adolescent%20dutifully%