was%20still%20in%20its%20infancy%2C%20and%20the%20existing%20products%20didn%E2%80%99t%20match%20the%20quality%20of%20cement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20two%20years%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20they%20created%20PLAVE%20(a%20play%20on%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98pavement%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98plastic%E2%80%99)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20unique%20construction%20material%20made%20from%20a%20blend%20of%20plastic%20waste%20and%20demolition%20debris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Patel%20and%20Nitin%20Yadav%20in%20their%20plastic%20recycling%20facility.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-1200x675.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_20241119_172305_7303-3-1732198244-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381949%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20waste%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20pile%20up%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gets%20used%2C%20it%20gets%20recycled%2C%20and%20it%20becomes%20a%20part%20of%20something%20new.%E2%80%9D-%20Rishabh%20Patel%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPLAVE%20was%20designed%20so%20that%20waste%20is%20not%20only%20consumed%20but%20transformed%20into%20a%20product%20that%20can%20be%20used%20again.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20win-win%20scenario%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rishabh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20win%20because%20we%20make%20money%20doing%20something%20good%2C%20the%20people%20we%20work%20with%20win%20because%20they%20get%20good%20products%20at%20a%20great%20cost%2C%20and%20the%20world%20wins%20because%20the%20work%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20is%20good.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20innovative%20products%20they%20have%20developed%20using%20this%20material%20is%20permeable%20pavement%2C%20which%20allows%20water%20to%20pass%20through%20it%20and%20aids%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357468%2Fias-officer-revive-water-table-cdo-varanasi-himanshu-nagpal-rainwater-harvesting-river-rejuvenation-groundwater-recharge%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20groundwater%20recharge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20helping%20to%20keep%20roads%20dry%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECommunity%20engagement%20and%20social%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20just%20business%2C%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20is%20deeply%20committed%20to%20social%20impact.%20A%20chance%20encounter%20with%20Parnika%20Shrimali%2C%20a%20Gurgaon%20resident%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20dispose%20of%20household%20plastic%20waste%20is%20now%20turning%20into%20a%20partnership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20finding%20out%20about%20the%20company%2C%20Parnika%2C%20who%20had%20some%20household%20plastic%20waste%20that%20she%20needed%20to%20put%20to%20use%2C%20contacted%20Rishabh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20to%20collect%20the%20trash%20and%20it%20was%20a%20very%20small%20amount%20compared%20to%20what%20we%20usually%20work%20with.%20But%20she%20was%20so%20passionate%20about%20not%20throwing%20away%20the%20trash%20mindlessly%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20take%20it%20off%20her%20hands%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rishabh.%20Parnika%E2%80%99s%20apartment%20complex%20is%20now%20collaborating%20with%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20to%20set%20up%20regular%20plastic%20waste%20collection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20and%20Nitin%20also%20wish%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20ragpickers%20%E2%80%94%20the%20unsung%20heroes%20of%20the%20waste%20management%20industry%20who%20often%20work%20in%20unsafe%2C%20hazardous%20conditions.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20spoke%20to%20them%20and%20tried%20to%20convince%20them%20that%20whatever%20you%20are%20doing%20in%20collaboration%20with%20different%20contractors%20is%20a%20different%20thing%2C%20but%20we%20would%20like%20to%20work%20with%20you%2C%20give%20you%20a%20proper%20place%20to%20live%20and%20just%20make%20the%20job%20more%20dignified%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rishabh%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PLAVE%20gaining%20traction%20and%20their%20waste%20collection%20operations%20expanding%2C%20Rishabh%20and%20Nitin%20are%20now%20working%20towards%20setting%20up%20a%20Material%20Recovery%20Facility%20(MRF)%20and%20are%20exploring%20new%20ways%20to%20reduce%20plastic%20consumption%20across%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20waste%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20pile%20up%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gets%20used%2C%20it%20gets%20recycled%2C%20and%20it%20becomes%20a%20part%20of%20something%20new%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rishabh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Dump%20In%20Bin%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732678200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D381912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rishabh%20Patel%20and%20Nitin%20Yadav%20are%20turning%20the%20tide%20with%20Dump%20In%20Bin.%20By%20focusing%20on%20the%20recycling%20of%20plastic%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20created%20a%20system%20that%20not%20only%20reduces%20waste%20but%20transforms%20it%20into%20valuable%20materials%20for%20industries%2C%20helping%20businesses%20save%20costs%20while%20contributing%20to%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381912%2Fdump-in-bin-plastic-waste-recycled-materials-plave%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20Imran%20Khan's%20PTI%20calls%20off%20Islamabad%20protest%20after%20government%20crackdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732678146000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115715591%2Cimgsize-1097622.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fimran-khans-pti-calls-off-islamabad-protest-after-government-crackdown%2Farticleshow%2F115715398.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115715398.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20called%20off%20its%20Islamabad%20protest%20after%20a%20police%20crackdown%20dispersed%20demonstrators%20from%20the%20Red%20Zone.%20Party%20leaders%2C%20including%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20chief%20minister%20and%20Imran%20Khan's%20wife%2C%20left%20the%20protest%20site.%20The%20PTI%20cited%20government%20brutality%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20suspending%20the%20protest%2C%20which%20initially%20aimed%20to%20secure%20Imran%20Khan's%20release%20from%20jail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fimran-khans-pti-calls-off-islamabad-protest-after-government-crackdown%2Farticleshow%2F115715398.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F