mg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20at%20home%2C%20my%20father%20sang%20a%20variety%20of%20classical%20compositions%20from%20different%20composers%2C%20and%20as%20he%20tells%20it%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20form%20and%20structure%20of%20about%2040%20ragas%20(musical%20modes%20in%20Carnatic%20music)%20with%20whatever%20limited%20syllables%20I%20could%20pronounce%20at%20the%20time.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20he%20observed%20early%20on%20that%20I%20had%20a%20%E2%80%98gift%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20such%20incident%20occurred%20when%20Varijashree%20was%20four%20years%20old.%20By%20this%20age%2C%20she%20was%20already%20delivering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F192140%2Fmysore-maharaja-wadiyar-western-classical-music-history-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclassical%20Carnatic%20music%3C%2Fa%3E%20vocal%20performances%20to%20small%20audiences.%20And%20this%20particular%20incident%20took%20place%20during%20one%20of%20her%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20concept%20of%20the%20concert%20was%20that%20I%20would%20sing%20for%20an%20hour.%20Many%20musicians%20attended%20this%20concert%2C%20and%20after%20my%20hour-long%20performance%2C%20they%20sang%20a%20set%20of%20compositions%20in%20100%20different%20%3Cem%3Eragas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20had%20to%20identify%20each%20%3Cem%3Eraga%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20I%20did%20successfully.%20This%20concert%20was%20filmed%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20person%20who%20recorded%20it%20lost%20the%20VHS%20tape.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FIaLqkeKx814%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20her%20beginnings%20as%20a%20child%20prodigy%20in%20Carnatic%20music%20to%20recording%20%E2%80%98A%20Rock%20Somewhere%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20inimitable%20Jacob%20Collier%20and%20Anoushka%20Shankar%20%E2%80%94%20nominated%20this%20year%20for%20a%20Grammy%20Award%20for%20%E2%80%98Best%20Global%20Music%20Performance%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Varijashree%20has%20undertaken%20a%20remarkable%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20musician%20with%20a%20classical%20foundation%20who%20has%20since%20expanded%20into%20diverse%20cross-cultural%20and%20interdisciplinary%20styles%2C%20this%20Grammy%20nomination%20feels%20like%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20not%20just%20this%20song%20but%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316118%2Fbengaluru-interactive-indian-music-experience-museum-bollywood-songs-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emusical%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20have%20undertaken%20so%20far.%20It%20is%20a%20milestone%20that%20reassures%20me%20that%20the%20direction%20I%20am%20taking%20%5Bcreatively%5D%20is%20good.%20Hopefully%2C%20this%20nomination%20fuels%20any%20independent%20artist%20out%20there%20to%20have%20a%20great%20and%20enriching%20creative%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMusic%20permeating%20through%20the%20walls%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarijashree%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%2C%20a%20master%20flautist%2C%20and%20my%20mother%2C%20T%20V%20Rama%2C%20an%20accomplished%20vocalist%2C%20were%20my%20first%20gurus.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20everything%20started%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20memories%20as%20a%20toddler%20are%20few%2C%20but%20they%20come%20back%20to%20her%20in%20flashes.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20vividly%20remember%20sitting%20through%20%3Cem%3EAppa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(father)%20flute%20lessons%20that%20he%20would%20give%20to%20students%20at%20home%20(he%20still%20avidly%20teaches%20to%20this%20day).%20Just%20being%20inside%20the%20house%2C%20I%20remember%20how%20the%20sound%20of%20my%20father%20playing%20the%20flute%20used%20to%20permeate%20the%20walls%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varijashree%20is%20a%20grammy-nominated%20artist%20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_447955265_1002102964966619_4669891626163685840_n_1080-1732543778-240x30