ise%20hygiene%20during%20menstruation%2C%20the%20foundation%20gives%20women%20a%20comprehensive%20kit%20of%20essentials%20that%20includes%20underwear%2C%20garbage%20bags%20(to%20teach%20proper%20disposal)%2C%20antiseptic%20liquids%20for%20hygienic%20wash%2C%20and%20paper%20soaps%20to%20encourage%20proper%20handwashing%20habits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20kits%2C%20Project%20Kishori%20largely%20focuses%20on%20educating%20girls%20about%20their%20bodies%2C%20helping%20them%20understand%20the%20menstrual%20cycle%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20them%20to%20ask%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20covered%20over%20100%20schools%20within%20two%20months%2C%20both%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur.%20And%20these%20are%20remote%20areas%20where%20nobody%20ever%20goes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20mentions.%20Through%20this%20outreach%2C%20Prazna%20has%20already%20educated%20over%2020%2C000%20women%20on%20menstruation%20and%20hygiene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20Project%20Kishori%20is%20its%20approach%20to%20breaking%20down%20the%20taboos%20around%20menstruation%20through%20peer-to-peer%20interaction.%20In%20each%20school%2C%20%E2%80%98Kishori%20Clubs%E2%80%99%20were%20established%2C%20bringing%20together%20girls%20who%20would%20lead%20conversations%20and%20share%20their%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20girls%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20get%20their%20periods%20young%2C%20get%20very%20nervous.%20They%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%20What%20Prazna%20and%20Preeti%20do%20is%20give%20a%20certain%20sense%20of%20reassurance%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%C2%A0%20Kavita%20Sharma%2C%20principal%20of%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3