%3EMaking%20men%20a%20part%20of%20the%20conversation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20inspiring%20aspects%20of%20Prazna%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20the%20way%20they%E2%80%99ve%20involved%20male%20teachers%20and%20male%20students%20in%20the%20conversation.%20Historically%2C%20menstruation%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20topic%20for%20women%20only%20which%20makes%20it%20an%20isolating%20%E2%80%98us%20and%20them%E2%80%99%20experience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20gone%20to%20a%20government%20school%2C%20and%20a%20teacher%20asked%20us%20to%20include%20the%20boys%20of%20the%20class%20in%20the%20workshop%20as%20well.%20And%20we%20were%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20include%20this%20idea%20in%20our%20manner%20of%20working%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20notes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMale%20teachers%20and%20volunteers%20have%20also%20been%20involved%20in%20workshops%2C%20breaking%20down%20barriers%20of%20shame%20and%20making%20the%20topic%20more%20inclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20have%20been%20encouraging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20kind%20of%20knew%20what%20menstruation%20was.%20But%20earlier%2C%20I%20used%20to%20feel%20hesitant%20to%20speak%20about%20these%20things%2C%20especially%20at%20home.%20I%20used%20to%20feel%20that%20maybe%20this%20is%20something%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20kept%20a%20secret.%20But%20then%20when%20we%20saw%20our%20teachers%2C%20and%20people%20from%20Prazna%2C%20speak%20about%20these%20things%2C%20that%20hesitancy%20has%20gone%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sonali%2C%20a%20Class%2010%20student%20from%20Jaipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20grassroots%20work%2C%20Prazna%20also%20advocates%20for%20comprehensive%20national%20policies.%20While%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20programmes%20which%20distribute%20pads%2C%20Preeti%20believes%20that%20menstrual%20education%20needs%20to%20go%20beyond%20just%20providing%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20good%20to%20give%20pads%2C%20but%20there%20should%20be%20a%20programme%20that%20happens%20at%20least%20every%20few%20weeks%20where%20the%20conversation%20is%20reopened%20and%20there%20is%20a%20continuous%20dialogue.%20Because%20a%20taboo%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20eased%20with%20a%20single%20workshop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%2C%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Preeti%20Sharma%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732512431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D381663%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prazna%20Foundation's%20Project%20Kishori%20is%20breaking%20the%20silence%20around%20menstruation%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20creating%20safe%20spaces%20for%20young%20girls%20to%20learn%20about%20their%20bodies%2C%20and%20talk%20openly%20about%20their%20menstrual%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381663%2Fmenstrual-education-prazna-foundation-jaipur-project-kishori-women-health-period-shame%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Plants%201%20Lakh%20Trees%2C%20Transforming%20Barren%20Land%20%26amp%3B%20Inspiring%20a%20Village%20To%20Embrace%20Green%20Living%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20time%20to%20plant%20a%20tree%20was%2020%20years%20ago.%20The%20second%20best%20time%20is%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20serene%20village%20of%20Sirkot%2C%20tucked%20away%20in%20the%20picturesque%20Bageshwar%20district%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20lives%20a%2060-year-old%20farmer%20whose%20life%20story%20is%20an%20inspiring%20testament%20to%20perseverance%2C%20dedication%2C%20and%20environmental%20stewardship.%20Jagdish%20Chandra%20Kuniyal%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20the%20environment%20has%20not%20only%20transformed%2