biomedical%20design%20at%20IIT%20Madras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExam%20D%3A%20A%20non-invasive%20solution%20for%20accurate%20diagnoses%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Vani%20and%20Vivek%20have%20three%20pet%20dogs%20each.%20As%20Vani%20argues%2C%20a%20major%20challenge%20in%20dealing%20with%20pet%20dogs%20is%20their%20high%20tolerance%20for%20pain%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20pet%20owners%20like%20her%20to%20recognise%20any%20real%20signs%20of%20discomfort.%20With%20a%20human%20child%2C%20you%20check%20their%20forehead%20to%20see%20if%20they%20have%20a%20fever%20and%20give%20them%20some%20soup.%20With%20dogs%2C%20however%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20touch%20their%20forehead%20and%20gauge%20whether%20they%20have%20a%20fever%20or%20not.%20Instead%2C%20you%20use%20devices%20like%20a%20rectal%20thermometer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVETiNSTANT%20replaced%20traditional%20rectal%20thermometers%20with%20a%20non-invasive%20device%20for%20diagnosing%20animal%20health.%20They%20also%20introduced%20a%20mobile%20app%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20pet%20parents%20to%20connect%20with%20veterinarians%20for%20timely%20diagnosis%20and%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-500x635.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vetinstant's%20non-invasive%20device%20for%20Pet%20Parents%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-500x635.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-236x300.jpg%20236w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvet-device-1732274942-15