0being%20demolished%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362584%2Fmedini-homestay-kaziranga-national-park-assam-sustainable-champak-deka-anna-louise-meynell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstruction%20of%20the%20cottages%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20recycle%20the%20cedar%20and%20pine%20wood.%20The%20roof%20lining%20details%2C%20bannisters%20from%20witness%20stands%2C%20and%20even%20whole%20doors%20and%20windows%20are%20originally%20from%20the%20old%20courthouse.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20six%20years%20for%20the%20dream%20project%20to%20see%20the%20light%20of%20day.%20But%20when%20it%20did%2C%20Palampur%20smiled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20cup%20of%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20a%20slice%20of%20sustainability%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20The%20Lodge%20at%20Wah%2C%20you%20name%20the%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eyou%20are%20in%20the%20mood%20for%2C%20and%20chances%20are%20it%20is%20grown%2C%20processed%2C%20brewed%20and%20served%20right%20on%20the%20land.%20During%20the%20tea%20tour%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20make%20an%20acquaintance%20with%20these%20different%20varieties%20which%20will%20give%20you%20an%20insider%20pass%20into%20the%20tea%20manufacturing%20process.%20Learn%20the%20nuances%20of%20tea%20production%2C%20including%20the%20processes%20of%20withering%2C%20rolling%2C%20fermenting%2C%20drying%2C%20and%20sorting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLodge-at-Wah-sustainable-travel-4-1732099435.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2