rding%20food%20diversity%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20know%20certain%20varieties%20of%20bean%2C%20rice%2C%20corn%20and%20pumpkin%20produce%20seeds%20that%20when%20stored%20in%20apt%20conditions%2C%20remain%20viable%20even%20centuries%20later%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarlapudi%20is%20cultivating%20a%20mini-revolution%20in%20his%20backyard.%20He%20is%20amused%20at%20how%20divergent%20the%20food%20habits%20of%20the%20past%20are%20when%20juxtaposed%20against%20their%20modern%20equivalents.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20grandparents%E2%80%99%20days%2C%20backyard%20kitchens%20and%20home%20gardens%20were%20used%20to%20grow%20vegetables.%20Today%2C%20their%20purpose%20is%20aesthetic.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Darlapudi%20dove%20into%20this%20newfound%20passion%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20new-found%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20always%20encouraged%20in%20my%20family%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20he%20felt%20the%20need%20for%20knowledge%20to%20back%20his%20pursuits.%20He%20registered%20for%20a%20training%20course%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277801%2Fhomaker-turns-farmer-earns-lakhs-with-organic-farming-kerala-mango-jackfruit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20farming%20methods%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Art%20of%20Living%20Foundation.%20The%20next%20two%20years%20were%20spent%20understanding%20the%20carbon%20content%20of%20the%20soil%20and%20its%20role%20in%20helping%20plants%20grow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1-1732015622.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20genetically%20modified%20seeds%20a