ce%20on%20monocultures%20and%20high-yield%20varieties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature%20(IUCN)%2C%20more%20than%20one%20in%20three%20tree%20species%20worldwide%20faces%20extinction.%20This%20genetic%20erosion%20is%20wiping%20out%20seed%20varieties%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%20And%20seed%20banks%20are%20a%20potential%20antidote%20to%20this%20problem%2C%20preserving%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20plant%20genetics%2C%20and%20providing%20a%20resource%20for%20reintroducing%20species.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Darlapudi%20breaks%20down%20the%20nuances%20of%20seed%20preservation%20to%20his%20audience%20of%20enthusiastic%20farmers%2C%20the%20process%20promises%20intrigue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darlapudi%20Ravi%20is%20preserving%20indigenous%20seeds%20that%20when%20planted%20will%20give%20rise%20to%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20loaded%20with%20health%20benefits%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDarlapudi%20Ravi%20is%20preserving%20indigenous%20seeds%20that%20when%20planted%20will%20give%20rise%20to%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20loaded%20with%20health%20benefits.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20we%20dive%20into%20that%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20understand%20why%20the%20practice%20is%20crucial.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20green%20revolution%20came%20the%20devaluation%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310545%2Fmp-lahari-bai-baiga-tribal-woman-preserves-rare-millets-seed-bank-ambassador-year-of-millets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20and%20native%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20genetic%20modification%20gained%20popularity%2C%20the%20genetically%20improved%20traits%20made%20it%20tough%20for%20the%20seeds%20to%20survive%20in%20adverse%20climatic%20regions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20seeds%20give%20quantity%20but%20not%20quality%2C%E2%80%9D%20Darlapudi%20says.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(local%20varieties)%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20two%20important%20qualities%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20sustain%20natural%20calamities%20and%20give%20a%C2%A0good%20aroma.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20says%2C%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20hybridised%20varieties.%20The%20first%20step%20of%20seed%20preservation%20is%20seed%20collection.%20%E2%80%9CI%20chose%20tribal%20areas%20that%20do%20not%20get%20much%20water%2C%20aside%20from%20a%20few%20hours%20of%20rainfall.%20This%20creates%20drought-resistant%20seeds.%20I%20collected%20seeds%20from%20the%20Pottangi%20area%20in%20Odisha%2C%20the%20Dantewada%20area%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Seethampeta%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Velur%20in%20Kerala.%20These%20include%20seeds%20of%20medicinal%20value%20and%20paddy%20varieties.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20collection%2C%20Darlapudi%20uses%20a%20varied%20array%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F189462%2Fdebal-deb-seed-bank-conserves-native-rice-variety-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreservation%20methods%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20range%20from%20potting%20the%20seed%20in%20mud%20or%20a%20bamboo%20container%20or%20applying%20soil%20to%20the%20seed%20and%20keeping%20it%20in%20the%20shade.%20But%20one%20of%20his%20favourite%20methods%20is%20coating%20the%20seed%20with%20ash.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20varieties%20like%20pumpkin%20or%20creepers%20come%20with%20slurry%20inside.%20Ash%20from%20burning%20dried%20cow%20dung%20is%20applied%20to%20the%20seeds%20and%20they%20are%20kept%20in%20bamboo%20containers%20or%20mud%20pots.%20This%20ash%20acts%20as%20a%20layer%20of%20protection%20for%20the%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20The%20seeds%20remain%20viable%20even%20after%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darlapudi%20has%20preserved%20over%203600%20varieties%20of%20indigenous%20seeds%20from%20tribal%20belts%20across%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381105%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDarlapudi%20has%20preserved%20over%203%2C600%20varieties%20of%20indigenous%20seeds%20from%20tribal%20belts%20across%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seed%20bank%20boasts%20over%2040%20varieties%20of%20rice%2C%20exotic%20vegetables%20such%20as%20red%20%3Cem%3Eokra%20%3C%2Fem%3E(lady%E2%80%99s%20finger)%2C%20black%20brinjal%2C%20pink%20beans%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekashi%20%3C%2Fem%3Etomato%2C%20red%20amaranthus%2C%20and%20aromatics%20like%20musk%20turmeric%2C%20%3Cem%3Earcka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(natural%20weedicide)%2C%20black%20basil%20and%20fragrant%20%3Cem%3Etulsi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20And%20Darlapudi%20ensures%20he%20uses%20natural%20farming%20techniques%20to%20preserve%20the%20seeds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20follow%20natural%20farming%20techniques%20while%20preserving%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseeds%20then%20automatically%20the%20seed%20germination%20value%2C%20and%20preservation%20and%20techniques%20of%20germination%2C%20will%20last%20longer%20and%20plants%20from%20these%20seeds%20will%20sustain%20through%20natural%20calamities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20over%20300%20farmers%20in%20seed%20preservation%20techniques.%20But%2C%20the%20legacy%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F176277%2Fkarnataka-bengaluru-organic-farming-native-seeds-woman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseed%20preservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20region%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20with%20him%2C%20he%20insists.%20It%20needs%20to%20be%20an%20ongoing%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20Darlapudi%20Ravi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiucn.org%2Fpress-release%2F202410%2Fmore-one-three-tree-species-worldwide-faces-extinction-iucn-red-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20one%20in%20three%20tree%20species%20worldwide%20faces%20extinction%20%E2%80%93%20IUCN%20Red%20List%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20IUCN%2C%20Published%20on%2028%20October%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsii.in%2Fimportance-of-seed-banks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImportance%20of%20Seed%20Banks%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Federation%20of%20Seed%20Industry%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732024705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-2-1732015773.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D381089%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Darlapudi%20Ravi%20was%20an%20assistant%20general%20manager%20at%20a%20cement%20industry%20when%20he%20realised%20how%20modern%20dietary%20practices%20lead%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20diseases.%20Here's%20how%20this%20realisation%20motivated%20him%20to%20build%20a%20seed%20bank.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A72%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381089%2Fseed-preservation-andhra-pradesh-darlapudi-ravi-indigenous-local-varieties%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Class%2012%20Student%20Builds%20Solar-Powered%20Agro%20Vehicle%20With%20Zero%20Carbon%20Emission%20for%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20tender%20age%20of%2017%2C%20Suhani%20Chauhan%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20student%20is%20making%20waves%20with%20a%20design%20that%20empower%20farmers%20by%20reducing%20production%20costs%20and%20boosting%20crop%20yields%2C%20helping%20them%20achieve%20greater%20efficiency%20and%20profitability%20in%20their%20farming%20practices.%20Her%20So-Apt%20Agro%20vehicle%20is%20an%20innovative%2C%20solar-powered%20farming%20vehicle%20that%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20farmers%20with%20potential%20to%20cut%20down%20carbon%20emissions%20by%202%2C72%2C000%20metric%20tonnes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%20was%20a%20Class%207%20student%20when%20a%20school%20field%20trip%20to%20the%20farms%20of%20Manesar%20ignited%20a%20spark%20within%20Suhani.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20the%20farmers%20toiling%20all%20day%20and%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20feel%20sympathetic%20for%20them.%20What%20shook%20me%20the%20most%2C%20though%2C%20were%20the%20heartbreaking%20statistics%20on%20farmer%20suicides.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20do%20something%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sight%20of%20the%20struggles%20sparked%20a%20determination%20within%20her%20to%20find%20solutions%20for%20the%20struggling%20agricultural%20community%2C%20particularly%20for%20small-scale%20farmers.%20Fuelled%20by%20a%20deep-seated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353629%2Fsocial-work-volunteer-for-ngo-social-town-helps-changemakers-raise-money-neenu-rathin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20for%20social%20ch%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353629%2Fsocial-work-volunteer-for-ngo-social-town-helps-changemakers-raise-money-neenu-rathin%2F%5C%22%3Eange%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20that%20ultimately%20led%20to%20her%20receiving%20the%20prestigious%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%20Award%2C%20a%20recognition%20bestowed%20upon%20young%20individuals%20who%20have%20made%20extraordinary%20contributions%20to%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3