%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20So-Apt%20Agro%20vehicle%20has%20a%20range%20of%20features%20to%20make%20farming%20easy%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20standout%20aspects%20of%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%20is%20its%20solar-powered%20design.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20inclined%20towards%20sustainability%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20was%20environmentally%20friendly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suhani.%20The%20vehicle%20operates%20entirely%20on%20solar%20power%2C%20which%20reduces%20the%20reliance%20on%20expensive%20diesel%20and%20petrol%2C%20a%20major%20cost%20burden%20for%20farmers.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352016%2Fhow-to-harvest-solar-energy-panels-in-apartments-homes-rentals-guide-to-save-electricity-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20panels%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20vehicle%20provide%20an%20energy%20reserve%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20other%20purposes%2C%20further%20enhancing%20its%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Suhani%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20there.%20She%20included%20a%20backup%20engine%20that%20can%20be%20used%20during%20the%20rainy%20season%20or%20at%20night%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20vehicle%20remains%20functional%20even%20during%20unfavourable%20conditions.%20This%20combination%20of%20solar%20power%20and%20backup%20energy%20makes%20the%20So-Apt%20vehicle%20a%20truly%20sustainable%20solution%20for%20farmers%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20So-Apt%20is%20set%20to%20transform%20agriculture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuhani%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20is%20evident%20in%20her%20design.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20country%20rich%20in%20solar%20energy%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20that%20harnessing%20this%20resource%20will%20be%20extremely%20beneficial%20for%20farmers%2C%E2%80%